data.description: Check out this great brick ranch on nearly a quarter of an acre in the heart of Fostoria! You'll love the large covered front porch! There is a lot of living space w/the generous-sized living rm, family rm & enclosed porch. The remodeled full bath is beautiful! Stainless steel appliances, pantry & peninsula seating in kitchen! The kitchen & family rm have just been de-wallpapered & painted! The 1st floor laundry rm includes the washer & dryer. Central air too! The oversized garage w/pulldown attic storage & 17x14 workshop off the back of garage complete the package! A sweet place to call home!
